server creation     = nodejs + express
---------------------------------------
basic comands 
-----------------

Creating of the package.json -npm init 
2)creation of the node modules - npm i express (installing of express)

Basic Steps
-----------
1)creating a folder Bank Server 
2) Create package.json
3) Install express 
4) Create index.js
5) create index inside js
6) Create an app using Express
7) Setup port number 
8) Resolving http request 
        get
        post
        put : update data partially
        patch : update data completely
        delete: To delete the data completely
9)Http response code 
        1xx - information 
        2xx - Successfull
        3xx-Redirection
        4xx-Client Error
        5xx-server Error

JSon web token

        install jwt - npm i jsonwebtoken

        To generate a token - sign()

11)Middle ware
        it comes in the middle of the request and response cycle of the node js execution process
                1)Application Specific middileware - for entire application
                        req ,res ,next

                              


                2)Router specific Middleware - validate -verify()-jwtwebtoken
                        
12) database intergration
        1)Install mongoose - npm i mongoose

13) Asynchronous function resolving - promise 
 
        1) Resolving state  -.then()
        2)Reject State - .catch()

14) CROS - Cros orgin Resource Sharing
        install Cros - npm i cors 



        port 4200 (angular)-----------request-------------> 3000 node

15) Asynchonous call -RxJs (Reactive Extensions for javscript)

JS -promise
TS RxJs(libray)

        1)Observable
                a)resolve - Subscribe()
                b)reject - catch
